<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <title>QuizLab</title>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
    <!--Add Bootstrap CDN and a link to jQuery-->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/3.4.1/css/bootstrap.min.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap-icons@1.11.3/font/bootstrap-icons.min.css">
    <!--Add Bootstrap CDN and a link to jQuery-->
    <script src="https://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/jquery/3.5.1/jquery.min.js"></script>
    <script src="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/3.4.1/js/bootstrap.min.js"></script>
    <style>
        .jumbotron {
            background-color: #0d6efd;
            /*Blue*/
            color: #ffc107;
            /*Lets make the jumbotron look good by adding some padding:*/
            padding: 100px 25px;
        }

        h1 {
            /*font-family: "Sofia", sans-serif;*/
            text-shadow: 3px 3px 3px #090404;
        }

        /*.bg-grey - adds a gray background color*/
        .bg-grey {
            background-color: #f6f6f6;
            /* Grey */
        }

        /*Align the description of the website*/
        .col-sm-8 {
            text-align: center;
        }

        .col-sm-4 {
            text-align: center;
        }

        .container-fluid {
            padding: 60px 50px
        }

        /*Set the size and color of the logos*/
        .logo {
            color: #0d6efd;
            font-size: 100px;
        }

        img {
            border: 1px solid #ddd;
            border-radius: 4px;
            padding: 5px;
            width: 150px;
        }

        /*Style the panels*/
        .panel {
            border: 1px solid #0d6efd;
            border-radius: 0;
            transition: box-shadow 0.5s;
        }

        .panel-heading {
            color: #fff !important;
            background-color: #0d6efd !important;
            padding: 25px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid transparent;
            border-top-left-radius: 0px;
            border-top-right-radius: 0px;
            border-bottom-left-radius: 0px;
            border-bottom-right-radius: 0px;
        }

        /* Bouton fleche */
        .btn-fleche i {
            transition: rotate 250ms ease-in-out;
            display: block;
            color: #0d6efd;
        }

        .btn-fleche.collapsed i {
            rotate: 180deg;
        }

        #ch.collapse,
        #meth.collapse,
        #phy.collapse {
            padding-bottom: 20px;
        }

        #Services.container-fluid {
            padding: 25px;
        }

        /*Style the footer*/
        footer .glyphicon {
            font-size: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            color: #0d6efd;
        }

        /*Style the carousel in CSS*/
        .carousel-control.right,
        .carousel-control.left {
            background-image: none;
            color: #0d6efd;
        }

        .carousel-indicators li {
            border-color: #0d6efd;
        }

        .carousel-indicators li.active {
            background-color: #0d6efd;
        }

        .item h4 {
            font-size: 19px;
            line-height: 1.375em;
            font-weight: 400;
            font-style: italic;
            margin: 70px 0;
        }

        /*Style the navbar*/
        .navbar {
            margin-bottom: 0;
            background-color: #0d6efd;
            z-index: 9999;
            border: 0;
            font-size: 12px !important;
            line-height: 1.42857143 !important;
            letter-spacing: 4px;
            border-radius: 0;
        }

        .navbar li a,
        .navbar .navbar-brand {
            color: #fff !important;
        }

        .navbar-nav li a:hover,
        .navbar-nav li.active a {
            color: #0d6efd !important;
            background-color: #fff !important;
        }

        .navbar-default .navbar-toggle {
            border-color: transparent;
            color: #fff !important;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body id="myPage">
    <!--Add a navbar at the top of the page that collapses on smaller screens:-->
    <nav class="navbar navbar-default navbar-fixed-top">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="navbar-header">
                <button type="button" class="navbar-toggle" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#myNavbar">
                    <span class="icon-bar"></span>
                    <span class="icon-bar"></span>
                    <span class="icon-bar"></span>
                </button>
                <a class="navbar-brand" href="#myPage">Logo</a>
            </div>
            <div class="collapse navbar-collapse" id="myNavbar">
                <ul class="nav navbar-nav navbar-right">
                    <li><a href="#À propos">À PROPOS</a></li>
                    <li><a href="#Matières">EXAMENS</a></li>
                    <li><a href="#Services">SERVICES</a></li>
                    <!--Revenir a laccueil ici-->
                    <li><a href="/">PAGE D'ACCUEIL</a></li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
    </nav>
    <section class="jumbotron text-center"> <!--Add the .text-center class to center the text inside-->
        <h1>QuizLab</h1>
        <p>Séries de tests pour les cégepiens</p>
    </section>
    <section id="À propos" class="container-fluid bg-grey">
        <!--Separate the icon and the "about text" by creating two columns (.col-sm-8 and .col-sm-4)-->
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-sm-8">
                <h2>Bienvenue sur l'interface classique!</h2>
                <p>Vous pouvez faire des tests ainsi que consulter vos résultats.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="col-sm-4">
                <!--Logo lit-->
                <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-education logo"></span>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
    <!--Add Matières container-->
    <section id="Matières" class="container-fluid">
        <div class="text-center">
            <h2>Tests</h2>
            <h4>Voici les tests que vous pouvez faire et dont vous pouvez consulter vos résultats :</h4>
        </div>
        <div class="row">
            <form action="/acces-quiz" method="post">
                <div class="col-sm-4">
                    <div class="panel panel-default text-center">
                        <div class="panel-heading">
                            <h2>Chimie</h2>
                        </div>
                        <button type="button" class="btn btn-fleche collapsed" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#ch">
                            <i class="bi bi-chevron-up"></i>
                        </button>
                        <div id="ch" class="collapse">
                            <h3>Chimie I (générale)</h3>
                            <img src="/general.png">
                            <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary d-inline-flex" name="nomQuiz" value="Chimie générale">Faire le test</button>
                            <h4><%user.scores[0]%>/10</h4>
                            <h3>Chimie II (des solutions)</h3>
                            <img src="/solutions.png">
                            <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary d-inline-flex" name="nomQuiz" value="Chimie des solutions">Faire le test</button>
                            <h4><%user.scores[1]%>/10</h4>
                            <h3>Chimie III (organique)</h3>
                            <img src="/organic.png">
                            <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary d-inline-flex" name="nomQuiz" value="Chimie organique">Faire le test</button>
                            <h4><%user.scores[2]%>/10</h4>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-sm-4">
                    <div class="panel panel-default text-center">
                        <div class="panel-heading">
                            <h2>Mathématiques</h2>
                        </div>
                        <button type="button" class="btn btn-fleche collapsed" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#meth">
                            <i class="bi bi-chevron-up"></i>
                        </button>
                        <div id="meth" class="collapse">
                            <h3>Calcul I (différentiel)</h3>
                            <img src="/derivee.png">
                            <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary d-inline-flex" name="nomQuiz" value="Calcul différentiel">Faire le test</button>
                            <h4><%user.scores[3]%>/10</h4>
                            <h3>Calcul II (intégral)</h3>
                            <img src="/huves.png">
                            <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary d-inline-flex" name="nomQuiz" value="Calcul intégral">Faire le test</button>
                            <h4><%user.scores[4]%>/10</h4>
                            <h3>Mathématiques discrètes</h3>
                            <img src="/discrete.png">
                            <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary d-inline-flex" name="nomQuiz" value="Mathématiques discrètes">Faire le test</button>
                            <h4><%user.scores[5]%>/10</h4>
                            <h3>Algèbre linéaire et vectorielle</h3>
                            <img src="/linear.png" class="btn btn-primary d-inline-flex">
                            <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary d-inline-flex" name="nomQuiz" value="Algèbre linéaire et vectorielle">Faire le test</button>
                            <h4><%user.scores[6]%>/10</h4>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-sm-4">
                    <div class="panel panel-default text-center">
                        <div class="panel-heading">
                            <h2>Physique</h1>
                        </div>
                        <button class="btn btn-fleche collapsed" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#phy">
                            <i class="bi bi-chevron-up"></i>
                        </button>
                        <div id="phy" class="collapse">
                            <h3>Physique I (mécanique)</h3>
                            <img src="/mechanics.png">
                            <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary d-inline-flex" name="nomQuiz" value="Mécanique">Faire le test</button>
                            <h4><%user.scores[7]%>/10</h4>
                            <h3>Physique II (électrique et magnétique)</h3>
                            <img src="/elec.png">
                            <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary d-inline-flex" name="nomQuiz" value="Électricité et magnétisme">Faire le test</button>
                            <h4><%user.scores[8]%>/10</h4>
                            <h3>Physique III (ondulatoire et moderne)</h3>
                            <img src="/waves.png">
                            <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary d-inline-flex" name="nomQuiz" value="Ondes et physique moderne">Faire le test</button>
                            <h4><%user.scores[9]%>/10</h4>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </form>
        </div>
    </section>
    <section id="Services" class="container-fluid bg-grey">
        <div id="myCarousel" class="carousel slide text-center" data-ride="carousel">
            <h2>Autres services</h2>
            <ol class="carousel-indicators">
                <li data-target="#myCarousel" data-slide-to="0" class="active"></li>
                <li data-target="#myCarousel" data-slide-to="1"></li>
                <li data-target="#myCarousel" data-slide-to="2"></li>
            </ol>
            <div class="carousel-inner" role="listbox">
                <div class="item active">
                    <h4>Si vous avez des questions,<br><span style="font-style:normal;"></span></h4>
                </div>
                <div class="item">
                    <h4>Ou si vous rencontrez des problèmes techniques,<br><span style="font-style:normal;"></span></h4>
                </div>
                <div class="item">
                    <h4>Contactez-nous au (514)809-6334. Il nous fera plaisir de vous aider!
                        <br><span style="font-style:normal;"></span>
                    </h4>
                </div>
            </div>
            <a class="left carousel-control" href="#myCarousel" role="button" data-slide="prev">
                <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-chevron-left" aria-hidden="true"></span>
                <span class="sr-only">Previous</span>
            </a>
            <a class="right carousel-control" href="#myCarousel" role="button" data-slide="next">
                <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-chevron-right" aria-hidden="true"></span>
                <span class="sr-only">Next</span>
            </a>
        </div>
    </section>
    <!--Add an "Up Arrow" icon to the footer, which will take the user to the top of the page when clicked on-->
    <footer class="container-fluid text-center">
        <a href="#myPage" title="To Top">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-chevron-up"></span>
        </a>
    </footer>
</body>

<html>